  "texts": [
    "These chunks were then embedded into a vector database using OpenAI's ada-002 embedding model, creating vector representations for similarity search and retrieval.",
    "The embedded chunks and their original text were stored as key-value pairs in a database, facilitating the identification of the top-k chunks most semantically similar to a given query's embedding.",
    "Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) with LlamaIndexLlamaIndex enhanced GPT-3.5 Turbo and GPT-4's accuracy by providing targeted context (EHR text chunks) through Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG).",
    "We created a retrieval system that selects the top-k relevant text passages for a given query.",
    "For each criterion, we set k = 5 and used the LLM prompt as the document retrieval search query."
  ]
